 up reading for a few weeks, if need be....<br />Then I asked myself...<br />“WHO DO YOU REALLY NEED RIGHT NOW?” <br />“What authors — have kept me interested in their books?”<br />Paul Auster came through! <br />Thank you!!! <br />This was just what I needed!<br /><br />Loved it!!!</span>
